"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-28-Medal-events-to-watch-at-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics-on-July-28-1vBFqF0FyRa-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  A total of 13 gold medals will be decided on July 28 at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN Sports Scene recommends the following competitions:  First, the women's skateboarding street final will take place at the Place de la Concord at 17:00 (GMT+2).\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concord_Records\", \"score\": 0.6533787839241794, \"rank\": 0.509511953580005, \"text\": \"Concord\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concord_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concord_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than a quarter-hour later, the women's archery team final will be contested at Les Invalides at 17:11 (CMT+2).\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then at 20:30 (GMT+2), two of the most eye-catching swimming events of the day \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 the men's 400-meter individual medley final and women's 100-meter butterfly final \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 will get underway at the Olympic Aquatics Centre in the Paris La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And at 22:15 (GMT+2) at the Grand Palais, the best-performing fencer will win the men's epee individual gold medal.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE